title: That Metal Show S09E01 Slash, Sam Dunn.mkv
description: Slash is interviewed and talks about Guns N' Roses being nominated for the Rock & Roll Hall of Fame, his fondness of live albums and snakes and the status of Velvet Revolver; Sam Dunn is interviewed and talks about his new VH1 Classic series Metal Evolution; in the Throwdown the guests and hosts debate which Guns N' Roses album is the best: Use Your Illusion I or Use Your Illusion II; in the Top 5 the hosts put together their definitive list of bands that should be in the Rock & Roll Hall of Fame; guest bassist features Glenn Hughes from Black Country Communion.
